Package com.ecom.listeners

package com.ecom.listeners
Provides classes for implementing various listeners in the application.

This package contains classes that implement TestNG listeners to perform various actions during test execution in the application. Listeners are used to monitor test execution and report test results.

The main classes in this package include:

  • ListenersClass: Implements TestNG's ITestListener and ISuiteListener interfaces for listening to test and suite events and generating corresponding reports.
  • AnnotationTransformer: Implements TestNG's IAnnotationTransformer interface for transforming test annotations during runtime.
  • MethodInterceptor: Implements TestNG's IMethodInterceptor interface for intercepting test methods and performing actions before test execution.
  • RetryFailedTests: Implements TestNG's IRetryAnalyzer interface * for retrying test methods based handler input when test got failed.
